rows.label: tlk42360112_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Right all clear! Left all clear!
Front all clear! All all clear!

rows.label: tlk42360112_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Lomlom checking place from top to
bottom to make sure Goldmund
running like clockwork!

rows.label: tlk42360112_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Slightest sight of damage or danger
and Lomlom run to fix it on the spot!

rows.label: tlk42360112_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Lomlom devoting self to maintenance
is for safety of all Goldmund, so
always determined to give best effort!
